      "rationale": "Validation conducted on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry identical to COU device. Blood analog properties matched. Operating range (3–6 LPM, 2500–3500 RPM) encompasses full COU operating envelope. Validation activities directly support credibility of COU predictions without extrapolation beyond validated domain."
