    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with documented justification. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts relative hemolysis index within 10% of experimental values across the full COU operating envelope. RH < 1 acceptance criterion met at all five operating points. The model is accepted as sufficiently credible for the stated context of use: identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device for regulatory submission.",
